1.3
log
@Remove the `skip splraise/splx for IPL_NONE mutexes' optimizations. It is not
always gaining anything, and msleep() implementation depends upon mtx_leave()
invoking splx().
@
text
@d1 1
a1 1
/*	$OpenBSD: mutex.c,v 1.2 2010/09/28 20:27:55 miod Exp $	*/
